 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du\\u0161an_Mandi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Du\\u0161an_Mandi\\u0107\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Serbia captain Nikola Jaksic scored three times, and Radoslav Filipovic made 10 saves.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998657906507, \"rank\": 1.3420934557062512e-07, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serbia advanced to the semis with a 12-11 victory over Greece on Wednesday on Jaksic's perfect skip shot from deep with 3 seconds left.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998657906507, \"rank\": 1.3420934557062512e-07, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999891842891, \"rank\": 1.0815554729490497e-08, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next up is the winner of the second semifinal between Hungary and Croatia.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999897682, \"rank\": 1.0204826084015447e-11, \"text\": 