women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. played without Johnny Hooper after the attacker was ejected in the first quarter of the quarterfinal because of a brutality foul.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Hooper_(water_polo)\", \"score\": 0.9999935967498832, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Johnny Hooper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Hooper_(water_polo)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Hooper_(water_polo)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hooper's two-game suspension was reduced to one after an American appeal, and he is expected to play in the bronze-medal match on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1572, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nellee_Hooper\", \"score\": 0.5931585664673447, \"rank\": 0.6858898374009043, \"text\": \"Hooper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nellee_Hooper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nellee_Hooper\"}, {\"begin\": 1629, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Appeal\", \"score\": 0.9995200176042466, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American appeal\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Appeal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Appeal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No matter what, the result in this tournament's better than we have had in a long time,\\\" U.S. captain Ben Hallock said.\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Hallock\", \"score\": 0.9999954986289044, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Hallock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Hallock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Hallock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But we are not going to be happy with fourth.\\\"\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marko Vavic scored two goals for the U.S. in its semifinal loss.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marko_Vavic\", \"score\": 0.9999995288507053, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marko Vavic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marko_Vavic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marko_Vavic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hallock, Luca Cupido, Alex Bowen and Ryder Dodd also scored.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1955, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luca_Cupido\", \"score\": 0.999998568927709, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Luca Cupido\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luca_Cupido\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luca_Cupido\"}, {\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Dodd\", \"score\": 0.9943260429282851, \"rank\": 0.005661508266227393, \"text\": \"Dodd\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Dodd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Dodd\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We could not finish.\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what it came down to,\\\" U.S. center Alex Obert said.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Obert\", \"score\": 0.9999982363735489, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Obert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Obert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Obert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We could not put the ball in the back of the net.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are just a little bit short with it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hannes Daube was shut out, missing each of his five shots.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2182, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannes_Daube\", \"score\": 0.9999997305463147, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hannes Daube\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannes_Daube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hannes_Daube\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old attacker leads the U.S. with 17 goals in a breakout performance in his second Olympics.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. closed to 8-6 on Bowen's goal with 4:42 left in the third quarter, but the Americans were shut out the rest of the way.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2372, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Bowen\", \"score\": 0.9993331034856392, \"rank\": 0.0006372926874262698, \"text\": \"Bowen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Bowen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Bowen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dedovic and Jaksic scored in the fourth to help put it away.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today was the night of the Nikolas,\\\" Jaksic said.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully it gets even better in two days.\\\"\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 MediaNews Group\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2666